tika.dc.description: The angel, Kellareal, stopped the genocide of a hundred and forty three human/animal hybrids, who'd been bred as a research experiment and spent their entire lives imprisoned. Against orders, he spirited them away to a dimension and gave them the job of protecting humans whose own hybrid experiment had escaped and become their nightmare. Rosie asked for a timeout, but never expected Carnal.
tika.dc.publisher: dba 7th House, Imprint of Andromeda LLC
